short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: displays default TimeZone in Google Calendar

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension enhances the Google Calendar web-interface.
It displays the GCal Default TimeZone in the upper-right, beside your account logo.
It is shown in the Calendar view as well as the Event view.
